{"tid":2486211,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚 老母西 IG:Aphrodite.r (4) 善用不推文回覆 頭號杯葛LF及嘉丹","createTime":"2021-04-12T17:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T20:19:38.000Z","uid":226337,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"75cb6ac1bac4b33512a228dd34a1c4ce3b2ef483","tid":2486211,"uid":226337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T17:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\">重推一次老母事跡<br />\n以免各位妹豬及絲打中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIG: Aphrodite.r 又名老母 著名ig界頭號begger<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">老母&amp;fds只會大話連篇 佢地推乜都唔好信唔好買</span> </span><br />\n<br />\n叫做老母因為佢個樣長到好似小新老母<br />\n而且又好鍾意用蠟筆小新<br />\n每日就喺Q&amp;A度打飛機當自己係女神<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYCfq6Vy3tLJv5Ta4boM9HkovzBwMeDcsURgmoMegpuwD?filename=BqvhVKF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBqvhVKF.png&h=c9c9d94d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYyKnqLdELqfxqga8QbwnAGTAUM8eUKHUNCi8G51irSdb?filename=nsNXbhg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnsNXbhg.png&h=9bf370f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVmdVzxssQSyMrqNHvASt1sU75Uu5XpowkBBpEoVvj6BE?filename=05rANiM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05rANiM.jpg&h=f9a2a0c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>老母十宗罪</strong><br />\n1.白鴿眼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nQ&amp;A時多次強調自己一定唔係住新界呢d窮人地方<br />\n(後有絲打補充佢住慈雲山公屋 比痴線西踢爆後又有絲打補充話轉左去私樓地址)<br />\n<br />\n2.乞衣性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n曾有疑似PR絲打話老母最鍾意周圍DM唔同BRAND 尋找合作機會<br />\n要求大量試用產品<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>之前 痴線西 狙擊笑9佢長黑碎髮勁村姑<br />\n第日老母乞衣到 即出story摸d頭髮 勁作狀<br />\n扮撚晒蟹咁(嘟嘴)：唔知幾時剪頭髮好<br />\n想乞salon幫佢免費整頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n3.蝗味濃無禮貌，加上當SA係狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成名事跡<br />\n因比follower QnA 問一問點解chanel 19格仔紋同官網唔一樣而起鋼<br />\n拎住個殘過梅菜ge chanel 19去返專門店同SA對質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全程story都係閪語氣<br />\n最近見比痴線西笑佢個袋似梅菜 就開始狂post story乞求內袋R下shop <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傳聞已經比唔小分行chanel SA討論中<br />\n<br />\n留完貨之後唔想要就post上story好似想拖捨大家咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTt3s2H3GwbiU6ycGubZNeATcNvfxdSUWXzzLTYLdT3dC?filename=9nmpALV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9nmpALV.png&h=4bfe8805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲成日去名店自拍打卡 但係從來唔見佢買袋<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZwpqNvKYQpWp6gNFCEdWevnz7Qde8e99qcNRJSdYWVBY?filename=TpEZuxo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTpEZuxo.png&h=cc715c82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 不停hardsell賺錢<br />\n使用護膚品速度異於常人地快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n膚質每天改變 乾肌每日都做deep clean<br />\n但係有時又話自己係插秧毛孔 無人知佢真實膚質係咩<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">有絲打懷疑係為左sell code而倒大量製造empty去證明自己說服力</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQreCtPRpBEtEUcrwheKUddqJtUaadPxMTpjU8gi3VxmY?filename=LFVVd88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLFVVd88.png&h=0687f2ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年度最愛post有超過50件至愛產物 絕大部份係試用 超過一半有affiliate code<br />\n只要係sponsor試用aff 都只會有讚無彈<br />\n<br />\n而且為左HARD SELL薄身PHILOSOPHY BODY LOTION<br />\n即使已出埋火災警告 濕度得45% 依然話天氣潮濕<br />\n<br />\n5. 每日打倒昨天的我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsell產品果陣就係咁話我要衝了好正呀好好用好抵買<br />\n賣完就無得再水人買就即時屌件野好差唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出post叫人茶護膚油然後轉頭story就sell控油野話自己好油<br />\n<br />\n以前話好鍾意the ordinary<br />\n但係而家未聽係the ordinary邊枝已經話無用<br />\n無sponsor就踩人<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfAxTW1qKBocf8zGdLpg8gndPd3TyXz5HVgDLF9CzY4qi?filename=wHbQGg7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwHbQGg7.png&h=f63abd26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcbJwjV3ShefdKP1S6cjP756NSePREnv5wb4k6zvahKR3?filename=dGirY3P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdGirY3P.png&h=698234ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 幫Korner賣鞋踩埋其他牌子 但係唔少絲打反映korner啲鞋唔好著<br />\n而且開live期間 兩條𡃁講緊嘢嗰陣老母係咁對撚住塊鏡睇自己<br />\n極自戀而且唔識禮貌同尊重<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdZBkWh5dvmiRsy9mHsNg4kRjkSwavSNcbyV1d54SY62g?filename=Kuh4BBU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuh4BBU.png&h=40799c9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf6HRifVnxjrTju662SCP6NBM9ePgzx5tHbziTgABxLN8?filename=4ZLeepD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ZLeepD.png&h=d7dc26c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 自稱白皮 但係開live見到另外兩條𡃁都白過佢<br />\n不停數臭朗豪坊chanel BA拎錯粉底顏色比佢<br />\n但係明明用最白色號嘅粉底都唔岩色<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX6QvHFTJLoaNnFmWgEi1McDJBkhgJ7duMTH19PVWxEzx?filename=5ujVLEy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ujVLEy.png&h=517fe15b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY8pZaj8QxLo9rCNH5GDGht5sCCiZ9VUqf8Jqq4XtCMDy?filename=FTLYJre.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFTLYJre.png&h=a1379653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. 自稱自己專業人士 BME 但英文極差<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaciMuNBXgQryJRc9pZ8T4FBgGRRbKT1Uwq6Re78nxHHX?filename=1i4uPU1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1i4uPU1.png&h=c770ebea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個arrange好闊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n9. Review P圖磨皮 連試色都要磨皮<br />\n有絲打整合咗放喺下面<br />\n<br />\n10. 以前用支那眼影仲要叫佢做國貨<br />\n就算係19年之前 正常人都唔會買支那化妝品啦<br />\n唔驚爛面咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇嚟老母係大劣人都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmerLEj6ohDWHospd6E2D5v9GUkZtwupjm3CNURejJo9JC?filename=5Ws1bNu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Ws1bNu.png&h=ee6df3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n11. 成日話自己買左乜買左乜<br />\n永遠淨係show shopping cart嗰個畫面<br />\n之後唔會見到開箱 除非係pr寄嚟<br />\n<br />\n12. 見qna人哋share男朋友會接送<br />\n佢就一句車埋去話 呢啲基本嘢有咩咁值得講<br />\n無禮貌唔抵得人好 但係之前成日話自己有ap夫唔比出樣<br />\n<br />\n13. 另外只要有其他人講佢推薦產品有缺點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即時全力拉埋幾個八婆朋友一齊狙擊阻佢搵錢ge仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n14. 熱衷上痴線西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次鬧老母ge cm都一定有一個負皮<br />\n近期Makeup Forever post (唔知係唔係廣告)<br />\n終於減弱filter露出粗大插秧毛孔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時吸收痴線西絲打意見 終於P短返塊面<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcX4XEkQHHWTfz13cgBfqZDc8NtALWpfnepB97xEVsuNV?filename=CLuFTwe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLuFTwe.jpg&h=71734d1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>老母日常</strong><br />\n1.一起身睇下自己仲係咪訓緊係公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.再上痴線西睇下今日風向 每個鬧佢ge comment留下負皮<br />\n3.然後諗下今日變咩skin type sell乜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁多支pr倒邊支野好????<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.再睇下邊個blogger話佢讚ge有code產品唔好用<br />\n全力狙擊阻佢搵真銀既仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\"