" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1wxXbFd.jpg&h=68e0a02c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且眼影都唔識blend就出街<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmdj2cvNcjMUkNoobmGKokJMf6fzLtrL1PG4FphCV1TWzY?filename=Lng5rLt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLng5rLt.jpg&h=2d105cef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTnFQZKCJWJK5X1MvEENriSbXsQRy51aKNiCkc3nsu8Rh?filename=jfNTADN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjfNTADN.jpg&h=7a66c0eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同老母一樣鍾意曬命 成日曬自己男朋友送啲咩比佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdgJFKQ1fYzwKq9ZR4gf3qoPpbNFq2d1fjkFgbuPaU2AQ?filename=kL4yuus.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkL4yuus.png&h=d63a1f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSELzcY6GBmhsejusvLZNZfr3oqdPfpFzMLt713c3Rkk6?filename=SxHHnPx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSxHHnPx.png&h=0b933b5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">青光眼巨人 @giant_sharing</span></span><br />\n對眼長期敏感咁 嚇撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經decorte碎粉一事 會今日話樣野好用 聽日又踩返佢<br />\n彈出又彈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">嚴重矽靈潔癖 惡撚過狗又醜樣<br />\n但有PR就即時唔再矽靈敏感</span></span></strong><br />\n借狙擊IG整合圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd2FEWhX9MtG7HEhxkmU8detswLPoaTSab9E2dG1wJz2B?filename=iwieJ7p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiwieJ7p.png&h=36cf7172&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWcY4VtP3cNnPGQcwCf2f4CF7kr9RYro9qCpr1uKYyKzj?filename=k4RcvNq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt